## Border  -0 means no border

	Additive:-(Adding Border to particular side)
	.border, .border-top, .border-right, .border-bottom, .border-left

	Subtractive:-(Removing Border from particular side)
	.border-0, .border-top-0, .border-right-0, .border-bottom-0, .border-left-0

	BorderColor:-(.border .border-primary)
	.border-primary, .border-secondary, .border-success, .border-danger, .border-warning, .border-info, .border-light, .border-dark, .border-white

	Border-radius:-
	.rounded-0, .rounded, .rounded-top, .rounded-right, .rounded-bottom, .rounded-left, .rounded-circle

## Clearfix (Quickly and easily clear floated content)

	<div class="bg-info clearfix">
	  <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary float-left">Example Button floated left</button>
	  <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary float-right">Example Button floated right</button>
	</div>

Note:- It provide space between two Divs

## Close Button

	<button type="button" class="close" aria-label="Close">
	  <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
	</button>


## Colors 

	Background:- .bg-
	.bg-primary, .bg-secondary, .bg-success, .bg-danger, .bg-warning, .bg-info, .bg-light, .bg-dark, .bg-white, .bg-transparent

	FontColor:- .text-
	.text-primary, .text-secondary, .text-success, .text-danger, .text-warning, .text-info, .text-light, .text-dark, .text-white

	Special Font Color:- (opacity)
	.text-muted, .text-white-50, .text-black-50

## Display

   hide:- .d-none(.hidden)   inline:- .d-inline         		flex:- .d-flex
   block:- .d-block			 inline-block:- .d-inline-block		inline-flex:- .d-inline-flex

## Embed

   Ratio 21:9 :- .embed-responsive-21by9
   <div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-21by9">
	  <iframe class="embed-responsive-item" src="..."></iframe>
   </div>

   Ratio 16:9 :- .embed-responsive-16by9
   <div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9">
	  <iframe class="embed-responsive-item" src="..."></iframe>
   </div>

   Ratio 4:3 :- .embed-responsive-4by3
   <div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-4by3">
	  <iframe class="embed-responsive-item" src="..."></iframe>
   </div>

   Ratio 1:1 :- .embed-responsive-1by1
   <div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-1by1">
	  <iframe class="embed-responsive-item" src="..."></iframe>
   </div>

## Float

    Left:- .float-left
    Right:- .float-right
    None:- .float-none

## Image Replacement (Replace Text With Background Image)

   .text-hide:-
   <h1 class="text-hide" style="background-image: url('/docs/4.0/assets/brand/bootstrap-solid.svg'); width: 50px; height: 50px;">Bootstrap</h1>

## Position

   relative:- .position-relative   
   absolute:- .position-absolute
   fixed:-    .position-fixed

   sticky:-   .position-sticky (div sticks when scrolling)
   static:-   .position-static (not compulsary)

   Top        Bottom       
   fixed-top  fixed-bottom   
   sticky-top

## Sizing (Height & Width)(In Percentage)
   
   Width:- .w-
   .w-25, .w-50, .w-75, .w-100
   Height:- .h-
   .h-25, .h-50, .h-75., .h-100
   Max-Width:- .mw-
   .mw-25, .mw-50, .mw-75, .mw-100
   MAx Height:- .mh-
   .mh-25, .mh-50, .mh-75, .mh-100


## Spacing (margin and padding)

   margin:- .m-, .mt-, .mr-, .mb-, .ml-, .mx-, .my-
   .m-0, .m-2, .mt-4, .mr-2, .mx-auto, .my-auto

   padding:- .p-, .pt-, .pr-, .pb-, .pl-
   .p-0, .p-2, .pt-2, .pb-4


## Text

   Text-Alignment:- .text-
   .text-justify, .text-left, .text-right, .text-center

   Text Wrapping:- .text- (.. in front of text)
   .text-nowrap, .text-truncate

   Text Transform:- .text- 
   .text-lowercase, .text-uppercase, .text-capitalize

## Font

   Font-Weight:- .font-weight-
   .font-weight-bold, .font-weight-normal, .font-weight-light

   Font-italic:- .font-italic

## Visibility

   Visible:- .visible
   Hidden:- .invisible

## Vertical Alignment (Aligning Text superscript subscript type)

   .align-baseline, .align-top, .align-middle, .align-bottom, .align-text-bottom, .align-text-top




